At 55, Korean model Jane is defying expectations and redefining beauty. Once scouted as a freshman studying ceramics at Kyung Hee University in Seoul, Jane graced the covers of top fashion magazines in her youth. But love led her down a different pathâ€”she left her modeling dreams behind to build a life and family in New York with her husband, a prominent financial executive and one of Koreaâ€™s most recognized finance influencers.

Over the past three decades, Jane cultivated her passion for abstract expressionist ceramics, raising two sons and establishing herself as a respected ceramic artist in the U.S. But her dream of modeling never truly faded. While studying fashion at the Fashion Institute of Technology (FIT) in New York, Jane prepared for her return.

And in 2024, she made a stunning comebackâ€”walking the runway at Seoul Fashion Week at the age of 54. Now, at 55, model Jane is back.

*   Self-Confidence and Self-Esteem: Participating in a beauty pageant can be a way to boost one's self-confidence and self-esteem. The process of preparing for and competing in a pageant can help individuals feel more comfortable and positive about their appearance and abilities.
*   Personal Growth: Pageants often involve various challenges and opportunities for personal growth. Contestants may develop skills such as public speaking, networking, time management, and grace under pressure.
*   Platform for Advocacy: Many pageants require contestants to choose a cause or platform they're passionate about. This gives contestants a platform to raise awareness and advocate for issues that matter to them, such as education, environmental conservation, or social justice.

title: Ladies beauty problems which they face in their daily life  Rosacea
description:
Ladies beauty problems which they face in their daily life  Rosacea

Rosacea is a chronic skin condition that is a common beauty problem faced by many women in their daily lives. It is characterized by redness, flushing, visible blood vessels, and sometimes acne-like bumps on the face, particularly in the cheeks, nose, chin, and forehead areas. Rosacea can be triggered by various factors, including genetics, environmental factors, certain foods, alcohol, stress, and hormonal changes. It can cause discomfort, self-consciousness, and impact the overall appearance and confidence of women.

This video is part 1 of the Defined (aka High) Cheek'bones' 3 part series. Subscribe and click the notification bell to get alerted when parts 2 & 3 are posted.

Jaw massage is an important first step for making more defined (aka high) cheek'bones.' Often we carry too much tension in the jaw, lower cheek, and chin areas. This pulls the midface downwards (less high cheekbones). For best results, the lower face massage & stretches should be done before parts 2&3 of the cheek'bone' series.

What I mean by defined (aka high) cheek'bones': More muscle tone in the upper cheek muscles enhancing the look of 'higher cheekbones'.

Gentlemen, let's delve into the world of fragrance and its role in the dating scene. Believe it or not, a cologne can be a game-changer when it comes to making a memorable impression on a date.

First and foremost, understand that cologne is more than just a pleasant scent; it's a tool for enhancing your attractiveness and leaving a lasting impression. A good fragrance can convey confidence, sophistication, and even sensuality, all of which are qualities that can greatly appeal to potential partners. This is not just a dating advice.

When selecting a cologne, it's essential to consider your own personal style and preferences. Think about the image you want to portray and the message you want to send. Are you aiming for something fresh and energetic, or perhaps something more warm and alluring? Choose a scent that resonates with you and complements your personality.

Now, let's talk about the ingredients that make up a good scent. While the specific combination can vary greatly, a few key elements are often found in powerful fragrances. Look for notes like citrus, woods, spices, and musk, as these can add depth and complexity to a scent, making it more intriguing and appealing.

When discussing fragrances, it's important to understand two key concepts: sillage and longevity. Sillage refers to the trail of scent that a cologne leaves behind, while longevity refers to how long the fragrance lasts on your skin. Both of these factors are important considerations when choosing a cologne, as they can greatly impact how others perceive you.

As for recommendations, there are plenty of options out there for men. It ultimately comes down to personal preference, but some popular choices include fresh citrus scents, woody and aromatic fragrances, and spicy or oriental blends. Experiment with different options to find the one that suits you best.

When it comes to date night, you'll want to choose a fragrance that exudes confidence and allure. Consider opting for something with warm and sensual notes, such as vanilla, amber, or musk. These fragrances have a captivating effect that many women find irresistible, making them perfect for setting the mood on a romantic evening.

In summary, don't underestimate the power of a good cologne on a date night. Choose a scent that reflects your personality and style, and don't be afraid to experiment until you find the perfect match. With the right fragrance, you'll be sure to leave a lasting impression on your date.

description:
I don't really pay attention to People magazine much. Sure, I might see an issue next to the checkout counter and think, "Huh, that guy from A Quiet Place is the Sexiest Man Alive." So, that is why it completely escaped me until like, last Friday, that Luke Combs was included on the Sexiest Man list. He was a part of the Sexy at Every Age category - where one man is picked for every age from 20 - 40-years-old. Combs ended up being selected for age 34; and folks around the country star, including his wife, have not heard the end of it. Turns out, Combs wasn't the only country star to make the list. Hunter Hayes and Warren Zeiders were also chosen for their respective age categories. 

Speaking of attractive people, several artists were asked who they considered the most attractive person in country music. Luke Bryan (trying to stay out of trouble) said Riley Green - who was also Bailey Zimmerman's pick. Meanwhile, both Sam Hunt and Riley Green agreed that Carrie Underwood was their choice.

title: Botox injections are a procedure used to soften the appearance of wrinkles and lines on the face.
description:
*Botox* injections are a popular cosmetic procedure used to soften the appearance of wrinkles and lines on the face, including around the eyes. 
*Here's how it works for eye wrinkles:*

ğŸ¯Botox is a purified protein derived from the bacterium Clostridium botulinum. When injected into specific muscles, it temporarily blocks the nerve signals that tell those muscles to contract.

ğŸ¯This relaxation of the muscles smoothes out the overlying skin, reducing the appearance of wrinkles.

ğŸ¯For eye wrinkles, Botox is most commonly used to treat crow's feet, the small lines that appear at the corners of the eyes when you smile or squint.

Facial Masculinization: Procedures for More Defined and Masculine Features
description:
Facial Masculinization: Procedures for More Defined and Masculine Features

Facial masculinization is a set of surgical and non-surgical procedures designed to highlight features associated with masculinity, such as a square jaw, prominent cheekbones, a straight forehead, and a defined Adam's apple. Ideal for transgender men or individuals seeking a more masculine appearance, this guide explores techniques such as jaw augmentation, forehead reshaping, chin implants, and thyroidoplasty (Adam's apple shaving). Discover how these procedures can harmonize your face and reinforce your identity.

Common Procedures:
Jaw Augmentation: Implants or bone grafts for a strong, angular jawline.

Forehead Reshaping: Augmentation of the frontal bone to reduce curvature and create a flatter forehead.

Chin Implant: Adds volume and projection for a more masculine profile.

Thyroidoplasty: Defines the "Adam's apple" for a more masculine neck.

Masculinizing Rhinoplasty: Creates a straight, wide nasal bridge.

Brow Bone Augmentation: Accentuates the supraorbital arch for a stronger look.

Non-Surgical Options:
Dermal Fillers (Hyaluronic Acid): To temporarily define the jawline or chin.

Botulinum Toxin: Reduces soft features (e.g., arched brow lift).

Key Benefits:
Defined Features: Strong, angular lines associated with masculinity.

Facial Harmony: Balance between bony structures and soft tissues.

Confidence and Self-Expression: Aligns your physical appearance with your gender identity.

Recovery:
Time: Depends on the procedure (1â€“4 weeks for surgical procedures; 0 days for non-surgical procedures).

Care: Avoid physical exertion, follow postoperative instructions.

Facial masculinization, jaw surgery, chin augmentation, thyroidoplasty, male rhinoplasty, male forehead, facial hormone replacement, masculine features, gender surgery, facial harmony.

title: Looks vs. Personality: The Balancing Act in Relationships
description: This podcast outline explores the complex relationship between physical appearance and personality in romantic relationships. It aims to discuss how these factors influence attraction, compatibility, and relationship satisfaction over time. The series covers a range of topics, including first impressions, cultural beauty standards, the importance of personality traits, the role of media, personal preferences, and the impact of implicit biases. The outline also emphasizes the importance of building holistic connections, nurturing inner qualities, and cultivating deeper connections beyond initial attraction. By combining personal stories, cultural insights, and expert perspectives, the podcast seeks to provide listeners with a meaningful framework for understanding and navigating the balance between looks and personality in their relationships.

description:
Unlock the secrets of a truly high-value man as I, Dr. Leslie, alongside Jamie Lynn, dissect the traits that define modern masculinity in the maze of dating and love. Grappling with the stereotypes that misunderstand attraction, we redefine what makes a man appealing beyond the surface. Our candid discussion navigates through the misconceptions men have about attractive women, and we set the record straight on the essential qualities like integrity, stability, and a non-aggressive expression of masculinity that constitute a genuinely high-caliber partner.

Embark on a thought-provoking journey with us as we confront the controversial ideologies of polyamory, the 'red pill' philosophy, and the often-overlooked phenomenon of toxic femininity. In an era where dating advice can be laced with manipulation, my eye-opening experience on the Rollo Show serves as a backdrop to our exploration of these contentious topics. We challenge the misguided tactics that promote control over connection and emphasize the strength found in vulnerability and emotional maturity.

As our intimate discussion unfolds, Jamie Lynn brings a therapeutic perspective to the complexities of dating after long-term commitments, the emotional intricacies of intimacy, and the profound personal growth that shapes our journey towards love. We share relatable stories and insights on navigating relationships with authenticity, setting boundaries, and the courageous act of honoring oneself. With an emphasis on readiness and intuition, we affirm the power of patience in finding a partner who resonates with our deepest values and desires. Join us for an episode that promises to illuminate the path to love with honesty and heart.

What is a Promotional Video?
A promotional video is a business video with the intent to promote your products and services to customers and prospects.

A good promo video seeks to bring the conversation to a more personal level without making the sales aspect so overt. Any video you create is in some sense attempting to sell your brand to your target audience. However, that doesnâ€™t mean itâ€™s a blatant sales pitch.

Youâ€™ve no doubt seen companies release videos in the past which celebrate an achievement or event, wish viewers a happy holiday, or tell their brand story. These pieces of content are promotional videos. Theyâ€™re transmitting information from the brand to the audience but without outright asking you to buy something.

If it helps, think of it this way: every video ad is a promotional video. Not every promotional video is a video ad. Diving into digital marketing can be like opening up a digital can of worms. For many, it can be intimidating. You know what, though? It doesnâ€™t have to be. Understanding the role which videos will play in your strategy can ease some of that intimidation. It helps to get you and your team on the same page. A good jumping-off point is to properly define just what a promotional video is. There are many types of videos you can produce for your business. From product videos and testimonials; to explainer and employee training videos.

But, letâ€™s make sure you understand the proper promotional video definition first!

Types of Promo Videos
When it comes to the kinds of promo videos you can create, you have a world of options.

Product videos
Intro videos
Product launch videos
Event videos
Explainer videos
Video ads
Recruitment videos
FAQ videos
Testimonial videos
â€¦ and more. There are quite a few possibilities when it comes to creating, so donâ€™t be afraid to think outside the box and get inspired.

5 Most Popular Celebrity Beauty Brands -  Rihanna, Kylie and Lady Gaga & More
description:
In the dynamic world of beauty, where trends evolve at the blink of an eye, celebrity beauty brands stand as formidable pillars. Leveraging the influence of renowned personalities, these brands redefine beauty standards, cultivate inclusivity, and inspire millions worldwide. In this comprehensive exploration, we delve into the realms of glamour and sophistication, unveiling the top five most popular celebrity beauty brands that have captivated hearts and adorned faces with their innovative products and empowering messages.

Fenty Beauty by Rihanna: Redefining Inclusivity and Innovation
Fenty Beauty, the brainchild of global icon Rihanna, emerges as a beacon of inclusivity and innovation in the beauty industry. With its groundbreaking launch in 2017, Fenty Beauty shattered norms by introducing a diverse range of foundation shades to cater to all skin tones. Rihanna's unwavering commitment to representation resonated profoundly, sparking a revolution that transcended traditional beauty standards. From the iconic Pro Filt'r Foundation to the shimmering Trophy Wife highlighter, each product exudes sophistication and versatility. Fenty Beauty's disruptive approach not only celebrates individuality but also fosters a sense of empowerment among its diverse clientele, making it a frontrunner in the realm of celebrity beauty brands.

Kylie Cosmetics by Kylie Jenner: The Evolution of Influence
Kylie Cosmetics epitomizes the meteoric rise of social media influence in the beauty sphere, spearheaded by the entrepreneurial prowess of Kylie Jenner. What began as a collection of coveted lip kits swiftly burgeoned into a full-fledged empire, captivating audiences worldwide with its trendsetting products and strategic marketing campaigns. Jenner's innate understanding of her audience coupled with her ability to harness the power of digital platforms propelled Kylie Cosmetics to unprecedented heights. From the velvety matte lipsticks to the mesmerizing eyeshadow palettes, each creation embodies Jenner's signature style and glamour, establishing her as a formidable force in the beauty industry.

Huda Beauty by Huda Kattan: A Global Phenomenon of Glamour
Huda Kattan's eponymous beauty brand, Huda Beauty, epitomizes the fusion of luxury and accessibility, captivating beauty enthusiasts across the globe. As a beauty influencer turned entrepreneur, Kattan's journey reflects resilience, passion, and an unwavering dedication to her craft. Huda Beauty's extensive lineup of products, including the iconic Desert Dusk eyeshadow palette and the velvety Liquid Matte lipsticks, exudes opulence and sophistication. Kattan's innate ability to anticipate trends and cater to diverse beauty preferences has solidified Huda Beauty's status as a global phenomenon, inspiring millions to unleash their inner glam.

KKW Beauty by Kim Kardashian West: Redefining Beauty Standards
Kim Kardashian West's foray into the beauty industry with KKW Beauty heralds a new era of beauty standards and self-expression. Renowned for her flawless complexion and contouring prowess, Kardashian West's brand ethos centers on enhancing natural beauty and embracing individuality. From the coveted CrÃ¨me Contour & Highlight Kits to the lustrous Ultralight Beams highlighters, each product embodies Kardashian West's signature aesthetic of effortless glamour. KKW Beauty's emphasis on simplicity, sophistication, and inclusivity resonates deeply with consumers, reaffirming the brand's position as a trailblazer in the beauty landscape.

Haus Laboratories by Lady Gaga: Empowerment through Self-Expression
Haus Laboratories, the brainchild of global icon Lady Gaga, transcends the boundaries of conventional beauty, celebrating self-expression and empowerment. Embracing Gaga's avant-garde approach to artistry, Haus Laboratories offers an array of bold colors, innovative formulations, and boundary-pushing products. From the mesmerizing Glam Attack liquid eyeshadows to the transformative Le Riot lip glosses, each creation empowers individuals to embrace their uniqueness and unleash their creativity. Haus Laboratories' commitment to inclusivity, diversity, and authenticity mirrors Gaga's ethos, inspiring a generation to embrace their inner beauty warriors and rewrite the rules of glamour.

Conclusion:

In the ever-evolving landscape of beauty, celebrity beauty brands reign supreme, wielding influence, innovation, and inspiration in equal measure. From Rihanna's trailblazing commitment to inclusivity to Lady Gaga's avant-garde celebration of self-expression, each brand encapsulates the essence of its founder, captivating audiences worldwide with its transformative products and empowering messages. As these brands continue to shape the future of beauty, they serve as beacons of glamour, sophistication, and empowerment, inspiring millions to embrace their unique beauty journeys and rewrite the narrative of what it means to be beautiful in a world of infinite possibilities.

description:
Men's hair styles 2022

There are many changes in hair styles that appear on a daily basis, in order to keep pace with the latest international fashion, so we find that men are constantly looking for iron forms of shaving and modern hairstyles, in order to appear with a distinctive and attractive look, which we will learn about as follows :

From simple menâ€™s hairstyles that depend on shaving the lower part of the hair, with a little gradual, reaching the highest area in the hair, leaving the hair long, and styling it back using a little moisturizing cream.

This haircut suits a man with a small forehead and very fine hair.

One of the menâ€™s haircuts that suit those with short hair, as this hairstyle depends on removing the hair from the bottom of the head while leaving a little of it gradually, and then a line is made on the side of the head.

The hair is left on top of the head in a symmetrical shape and a suitable length as desired, and it is styled using a little fixing cream, and the fingers of the hand, and the hair is combed back in the side of the head a little, which shows the man with a distinctive and attractive look.

A light and simple haircut for men, where the man reduces the hair on the entire head, taking into account the hair cut in the middle of the head without removing it, meaning leaving the hair short in the middle of the head, through which the short hair is styled using the brush and a little moisturizing cream.


 hairstyle is suitable for men who are interested in raising the chin, as it depends primarily on reducing the hair from the bottom of the head very little, leaving the hair from the top long, and styling it randomly to the front, and this story is suitable for the owners of slightly fine hair .

description:
What's your favourite finishing touch? 
When it comes to the ultimate finishing touch, the choice between enhancing your lashes or perfecting your lips can make all the difference. Lashes have the power to open up your eyes, creating a mesmerizing look that can be both subtle and striking, depending on your mood. The right mascara or a pair of false lashes can elevate any look, making your eyes the focal point. Alternatively, a bold lip color can convey confidence and style, instantly elevating your entire appearance. Whether you prefer the dramatic effect of well-defined lashes or the statement-making impact of a vibrant lip shade, both options allow you to express your unique style and finish off your look with flair.

Why Personal Grooming is ESSENTIAL for Men
description:
Why is Personal Grooming Important?
When it comes to grooming, most young men will agree that it should be part of their daily routine. So, what is grooming? It consists of bathing, shaving your facial hair, applying deodorant, getting a haircut, and other activities. It's a collection of habits and actions designed to give you a neat and tidy appearance.


One of our goals is to educate the gentlemen on the importance of grooming. Here are some of the reasons why it is essential for gentlemen like you.


#1 IT MAKES YOU MORE ATTRACTIVE
Man in a Blue Polo
First and foremost, grooming greatly improves your physical appearance. A GATSBY Gent who is clean and smells good will always be identified as attractive. Simple things like styling your hair with pomade and removing oil from your face every now and then can make a big difference in how you look.


#2 BEING WELL GROOMED IS VERY CONFIDENT. BOOSTER
Edward Barber GATSBY
Clean-looking people all have one thing in common: they exude confidence and good vibes. Being well-groomed makes it easier to navigate social gatherings and make new friends. Confidence is the foundation of a successful gent, so taking hygiene seriously is a good first step.


#3 YOUR FRIENDS AND PEERS WILL RESPECT YOU MORE.
Two men and a laptop
Did you know that cleanliness is commonly associated with intelligence? A well-dressed young man always makes a good impression on his classmates, friends, and those he meets for the first time. A true GATSBY gent takes pride in his appearance, which others will undoubtedly notice.

#4 GROOMING IS ONE OF THE EASIEST WAYS TO IMPROVE YOURSELF WITHOUT DOING MUCH WORK.
Gatsby Model fixing his hair
Personal grooming is the cheapest and most effective way to improve your overall style and appearance without spending a lot of time and money. Taking a shower, shaving, and using affordable, yet essential grooming and hairstyle products for men like GATSBY are all you need to stay on top of your grooming routine.

#5 TAKING CARE OF YOURSELF IS THE ULTIMATE FORM OF SELF-DISCIPLINE
GATSBY man reading a book
Personal hygiene is not difficult to maintain, but doing so on a daily basis is a real challenge for many people. Taking care of yourself on a daily basis will not only keep you smelling fresh and clean, but it will also improve your self-discipline and, more importantly, form good habits.

As previously stated, grooming does not have to be costly! That's why GATSBY is here to help you achieve your grooming goals without breaking the bank. Visit our website to view all of our products.

Small study ranks faces with and without masks, finds masked ones hotter
description:
Read full article here: https://readnews.io/siknmp



A small study found that people who wore face masks were thought of as more attractive, according to research from two universities in Pennsylvania. The project, which has been dubbed Beauty and the Mask, was conducted by Temple Universitys College of Public Health and the Center for Human Appearance at the University of Pennsylvanias Perelman School of Medicine.  With the help of 500 participants, 60 faces were ranked on attractiveness. MEN LESS LIKELY TO WEAR FACE MASKS BECAUSE THEY SEE THEM AS SIGN OF WEAKNESS, STUDY SUGGESTSThis study utilized a racially diverse set of male and female faces, which were sourced from the Chicago Face Database.  Participants were required to rank the faces without a mask and categorize them as unattractive, average or attractive. However, when surgical masks were digitally added to the faces, researchers found that participants upped their attractiveness rankings in statistically significant amounts for both women and men. CORONAVIRUS EXPERT SAYS AMERICANS WILL BE WEARING MASKS FOR SEVERAL YEARSThe faces that were previously categorized as unattractive reportedly saw the most improvement in their average rating at 42 percent. "Many people believe that the appearance of the eyes is one of the strongest influencers of judgments of attractiveness, said David B.  Sarwer, the associate dean for research and director of the Center for Obesity Research and Education at Temples College of Public Health.  This study suggests that aspects of the lower face, which are covered by masks, also play an important role in perceptions of attractiveness. "CLICK HERE TO GET THE FOX NEWS APPThe study also reiterated the long-held assertion that facial symmetry and harmony were key factors that play a role in attractiveness. Faces that had disharmonious facial features such as the nose, jaw, neck or lips had attractiveness rankings that skewed on the lower end of the spectrum,
